quran[9{c,v,t}:
48,1,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko fatah di. fatah bhi Sarih وصاف
48,2,taakay khuda tumahray aglay aur pichlle gunah bakhash day aur tum par apni Nemat poori kardey aur tumhe seedhay raste chalaye
48,3,aur khuda tumhari zabardast madad kere
48,4,wohi to hai jis ne mominoun ke dilon par tasalii nazil farmai taakay un ke imaan ke sath aur imaan barhay. aur asmano aur zameen ke lashkar ( sab ) khuda hi ke hain. aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
48,5,( yeh ) is liye ke woh momin mardon aur momin aurton ko bahishtoon mein jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain daakhil kere woh is mein hamesha rahen ge aur un se un ke gunaaho ko daur kardey. aur yeh khuda ke nazdeek barri kamyabi hai
48,6,aur ( is liye ke ) munhafiq mardon aur munhafiq aurton aur mushriq mardon aur mushriq aurton ko jo khuda ke haq mein buray buray khayaal rakhtay hain azaab day. un hi par buray haadsay waqay hon. aur khuda un par ghusse howa aur un par laanat ki aur un ke liye dozakh tayyar ki. aur woh buri jagah hai
48,7,aur asmano aur zameen ke lashkar khuda hi ke hain. aur khuda ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
48,8,aur hum ne ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum ko haq zahir karne wala aur khushkhabri sunanay wala aur khauf dilanay wala ( bana kar ) bheja hai
48,9,taakay ( mslmano ) tum log khuda par aur is ke paighambar par imaan lao aur is ki madad karo aur is ko buzurag samjhoo. aur subah vsham is ki tasbeeh karte raho
